name: Humbara
tag_list: latest-womens-fashion, cheap-clothes, womens-clothing, party-dresses, evening-dresses, clubwear, lingerie
overview: Since its formation Humbara became the World’s Cheapest but Quality Women’s Fashion Online Store. Every single item is sold for £5 ( 6 Euros - 7 Dollars ) or less Despite issues with finances and struggles They manage to gain a substantial number of customer base. Humbara targets 18/45 age range and delivers the best possible quality products. Profit margins are low and that reflects to annual turnover. If they can get the right finances and help There is no doubt that It will become the most successful Fashion Store in the World. It will be the facebook of fashion. Their fashion range includes; evening dresses, party dresses, cocktail dresses, clubwear, tops, trousers, lingerie, accessories and much more.
